{
    "json_version": 0x2,
    "name": "EVENT_MESSAGE_QC01_WIL_050.ebm",
    "nb_messages": 0x23,
    "messages": [
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x0,
            "msg_string": "Done! Hmm, and the quality is...<CR>Hmhmhm, I guess it's not bad..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1be,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1,
            "msg_string": "I'm coming iiiiiin! Oh, are you in the middle of a synthesis?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x194,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x2,
            "msg_string": "No, no. I actually just finished."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x165,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x3,
            "msg_string": "Awww, okay. I kinda wanted to see you synthesize."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x167,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x4,
            "msg_string": "Hey, make something one more time for me!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x5,
            "msg_string": "Hehehe, sure. Let's do a simple ointment..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x6,
            "msg_string": "That's basically it. After I scoop out the supernatant liquid, it's done."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x169,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x7,
            "msg_string": "Whoa. You're better at this than I thought you were. I think I'm starting to see you in a whole new light."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x16b,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x8,
            "msg_string": "I guess you weren't just an airhead..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x9,
            "msg_string": "An airhead!? That's so mean..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xa,
            "msg_string": "But really, that was a good learning experience. I suppose alchemy is cool, too..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15a,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xb,
            "msg_string": "Alchemy...?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xc,
            "msg_string": "The image of us, witches, is that we extract effects from catalysts..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xd,
            "msg_string": "But alchemy extracts elements from catalysts and breaks down part of the materials for resynthesis."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0xe,
            "msg_string": "Hey. You can synthesize things other than medicine, right? What can you make?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15d,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0xf,
            "msg_string": "Umm...like, bread."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x10,
            "msg_string": "Bread!? With a cauldron!?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x161,
            "expr_id": 0x5,
            "msg_id": 0x11,
            "msg_string": "Yup. Bread simmered in a cauldron turns out crisp, yet fluffy and delicious."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x126,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x12,
            "msg_string": "Really? I can't even imagine simmered bread..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x127,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x13,
            "msg_string": "Alchemists are weird!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x15c,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x14,
            "msg_string": "...Umm, can I ask you something? Who are...alchemists?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x15,
            "msg_string": "Someone else asked me something about alchemy before... What are you guys talking about?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x128,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x16,
            "msg_string": "Huh? What do you mean?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x3,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x17,
            "msg_string": "Well, I mean exactly what I said..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x165,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x18,
            "msg_string": "No, really, what are you trying to say?"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x167,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x19,
            "msg_string": "Synthesizing stuff in a cauldron, like you just did, is performing alchemy."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x1,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1a,
            "msg_string": "And the people who can do that are called alchemists."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x7,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1b,
            "msg_string": "Therefore! YOU are an alchemist!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x122,
            "expr_id": 0x4,
            "msg_id": 0x1c,
            "msg_string": "What!? No, I'm not. I'm an apothecary."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1d,
            "msg_string": "An apothecary wouldn't simmer bread in a cauldron! That's totally an alchemist thing."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x124,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1e,
            "msg_string": "Hmmm...it still doesn't feel right.<CR>My grandpa was an apothecary, too..."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x1f,
            "msg_string": "I guess you lack awareness of being an alchemist... Fine."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x1,
            "name_id": 0x1,
            "extra_id": 0x2,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x20,
            "msg_string": "I'll give you something nice. Read this and educate yourself a little."
        },
        {
            "type": 0x1,
            "voice_id": 0x0,
            "name_id": 0x0,
            "extra_id": 0x1a5,
            "expr_id": 0x0,
            "msg_id": 0x21,
            "msg_string": "Is this an alchemy book? Wow, thanks!"
        },
        {
            "type": 0x2,
            "voice_id": 0xffffffff,
            "name_id": 0xffffffff,
            "extra_id": 0xffffffff,
            "expr_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_id": 0xffffffff,
            "msg_string": "You got the book: Alchemy Basics."
        }
    ]
}